metadata.name: Bored Of Work Club #1
metadata.description: The Bored of Work Club is a community-driven collectibles project for a decentralized community of like minded individuals and entrepreneurs. Bored of Work Club NFTs come in a range of colors, traits and variations with an overall collection limit of 10,000. Will you get an angry, tired or bored working Zombie. Will you get a family member roaming while you work or are you a Cat or Dog person?
